\", Announce ''Calm'' Album: See When It's Coming|last=Weatherby|first=Taylor|website=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|date=5 February 2020|accessdate=5 February 2020}}</ref>\n* Label: [[Interscope Records|Interscope]]\n* Format: CD, digital download, LP\n| \u2014 || 7 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 4</br><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/dua-lipa-claims-first-number-1-on-the-official-irish-albums-chart-with-future-nostalgia__29309/|title=Dua Lipa claims first Number 1 on the Official Irish Albums Chart with Future Nostalgia|last=White|first=Jack|date=3 April 2020|website=[[Official Charts Company]]|accessdate=3 April 2020}}</ref> || 5 || 4<br /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/albums?chart=4841|title=NZ Top 40 Albums Chart|publisher=[[Recorded Music NZ]]|date=6 April 2020|accessdate=4 April 2020}}</ref> || 1 || \u2014\n|\n|\n|-\n| colspan=\"15\" style=\"font-size:85%\"| \"\u2014\" denotes an album that did not chart or was not released.\n|}\n\n===Live albums===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:14em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:18em;\"| Details\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"8\"| Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Sales\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[ARIA Charts|AUS]]<br/><ref name=\"AUS\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Ultratop|BEL]]<br/><ref name=\"VL\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Syndicat National de l'\u00c9dition Phonographique|FRA]]<br/><ref name=\"FRA\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Irish Albums Chart|IRE]]<br/><ref name=\"IRE\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[MegaCharts|NL]]<br/><ref name=\"NL\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Official New Zealand Music Chart|NZ]]<br/><ref name=\"NZ\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:8