.11.2014 (wk47)|website=zobbel.de|accessdate=6 December 2014}}\n* For songs from the album ''5 Seconds of Summer'': {{cite web|url=http://www.zobbel.de/cluk/140712cluk.txt|title=CHART: CLUK Update 12.07.2014 (wk27)|website=zobbel.de}}\n</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Heartache on the Big Screen\"\n| rowspan=\"18\"| 2014\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 123 \n| rowspan=\"2\"| ''She Looks So Perfect'' (EP)\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"The Only Reason\"\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 143 \n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Wrapped Around Your Finger\"\n| \u2014 || 77 || \u2014 || 119 \n| rowspan=\"3\"| ''Don't Stop'' (EP)\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Rejects\"\n| \u2014 || 78 || \u2014 || 108 \n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Try Hard\"\n| \u2014 || 79 || \u2014 || 80\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Heartbreak Girl\"\n| \u2014 || 42 || \u2014 || 108\n| rowspan=\"10\"| ''5 Seconds of Summer''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"18\"\n| \u2014 || 45 || \u2014 || 127\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Greenlight\"\n| \u2014 || 53 || \u2014 || 169\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Voodoo Doll\"\n| \u2014 || 55 || \u2014 || 128\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Beside You\"\n| \u2014 || 56 || \u2014 || 129\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Long Way Home\"\n| \u2014 || 58 || \u2014 || 148\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"English Love Affair\"\n| \u2014 || 61 || \u2014 || 142\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"End Up Here\"\n| \u2014 || 65 || \u2014 || 170\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Never Be\"\n| \u2014 || 67 || \u2014 || 162\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Social Casualty\"\n| \u2014 || 68 || \u2014 || 157\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Daylight\"\n| 61 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 109\n| rowspan=\"2\"| ''Amnesia'' (EP)\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[American Idiot (song)|American Idiot]]\"\n| 89 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Just Saying\"\n| 54 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 133\n| ''Good Girls'' (EP)\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Broken Home\"\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2015\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 165 \n| rowspan=\"3\"| ''Sounds Good Feels Good''<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.zobbel.de/cluk/151031cluk.txt |title=CHART: CLUK Update 31.10.2015 (wk44) |website=zobbel.de |date=2015-10-31}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Catch Fire\"\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 177\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Permanent Vacation\"\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 140\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Lie to Me\"\n| 2018\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014{{efn|group=upper-alpha|\"Lie to Me\" did not enter the NZ Top 40 or Hot Singles Chart, but peaked at number six on the NZ Hot Singles Chart.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/singles?chart=4493|title=NZ Heatseeker Singles Chart|publisher=[[Recorded Music NZ]]|date=25 June 2018|accessdate=22 June 2018}}</ref>}} || \u2014\n| ''Youngblood''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Red Desert\"\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2020\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || 17 || \u2014\n| rowspan=\"3\"| ''Calm''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Best Years\"\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || 22 || \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Not in the Same Way\"\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || 20 || \u2014\n|-\n| colspan=\"18\" style=\"font-size:85%\"| \"\u2014\" denotes a song that did not chart or was not released.\n|}\n\n==Other appearances==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:20em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:1em;\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\"| Album\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[American Idiot (song)|American Idiot]]\"\n|2014\n| ''Kerrang! Does Green Day's American Idiot''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Take What You Want\"<br /><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">([[One Ok Rock]] featuring 5 Seconds of Summer)</span><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.knac.com/article.asp?ArticleID=22352|title=KNAC.COM - News - ONE OK ROCK Unveils New Album 'Ambitions'|website=knac.com}}</ref>\n| 2017\n| ''[[Ambitions (One Ok Rock album)|Ambitions]]''\n|}\n\n==Music videos==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:20em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:1em;\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\"| Director\n! scope=\"col\"| Views\